These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, light-blue, coral, brown
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic, musician, electrician
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, sunflower, poppy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, september, april
1. the person who growsiris is the electrician##1
2. the person who growssunflower is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes brown##2
3. the person who growsiris is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the dancer is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes coral##1
7. the mechanic is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
8. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | light-blue | brown   | orange  | coral  |
| Job   | mechanic    | electrician    | dancer      | musician    |
| Flower   | poppy | iris | sunflower | tulip |
| Birthday     | april  | may       | february    | september     |

