.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, orange, azure, black
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, accountant, firefighter, chef
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, pall-mall, oliveros
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, bridge, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the chef is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person playing scrabble##2
6. the person playing chess is between the chef and the oliveros-smoker##2
7. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the accountant is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
9. the firefighter is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | black | orange    | azure  | chestnut    |
| Job   | librarian      | accountant  | chef  | firefighter |
| Cigar           | oliveros      | pall-mall       | game      | prince       |
| Game         | billiard    | chess | bridge | scrabble |

