.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
House: cottage, gothic-revival, colonial, townhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, colombian, french, russian
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, rabbit, goldfish
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, mah-jongg, bridge
1. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the colonial house is on the left of the french##1
6. the owner of the fish is the russian##1
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the french##1
8. the cottage house is between the italian and the russian##2
9. the french is between the colonial house and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House        | gothic-revival | colonial     | cottage   | townhouse     |
| Nationality       | colombian   | italian   | french | russian |
| Pet         | dog   | rabbit | goldfish       | fish    |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | poker | backgammon  | bridge    |

