 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the spanish##1
 4. the indian is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the indian##1
 7. the person drinking water is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the chinese##1
10. the person who likes red is between the person traveling to paris and the person who likes aquamarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Color           | chestnut  | aquamarine | red     | fuchsia |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk  | milk | water       |
| City           | hamburg       | marseilles    | edinburgh      | paris           |
| Nationality         | indian | chinese   | spanish   | colombian         |

