 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is between the fan funk and the person driving the tram##2
10. the person driving the boat is the fan electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
