 8. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
10. the person eating eggplant is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
